title: NSA Hearing European Parliament 5 Sept 2013 (full).webm
description:
The full video of the NSA hearing in the Human Rights Committee (LIBE) in the European Parliament 5 September 2013. Courtesy European Parliaments AV Unit. (Sorry for the low resolution, but that is what we got.) With Jaques Follorou (Le Monde), Jacob Appelbaum, Alan Rusbridger (The Guardian), Carlos Coelho MEP, Gerhard Schmid ex-MEP & Duncan Campbell.
